        {"key": "tutorial.step1", "value": "Welcome to Empire of Cards!\n\nYour goal: dominate the market by controlling 6 out of 10 territories."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step2", "value": "These are your cards. You start with a basic deck of 14 cards.\nEach turn you draw 5 cards to your hand."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step3", "value": "Card Types:\n\nBlue = Business (earns money)\nGreen = Employee (boosts business)\nRed = Action (instant effect)\nPurple = Upgrade (permanent bonus)"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step4", "value": "Drag a blue Business card to an empty slot on the board.\nTry placing your Diner!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step5", "value": "Great! Your Diner now earns $50/turn and attracts 3 customers.\nMore customers = more market share!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step6", "value": "You have 3 actions per turn.\nEach card played costs 1 action.\nThe green dots show remaining actions."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step7", "value": "When you're done, press END TURN.\nThe system will calculate income, pay salaries, and update territories."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step8", "value": "Business Income - Employee Salaries - 15% Tax = Your Profit\nWatch your money grow each turn!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step9", "value": "The bar at top shows territory control.\nBlue = yours, Red = rival, Gray = unclaimed.\nGet 6 blue territories to WIN!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step10", "value": "MegaCorp is your rival.\nThey also build businesses and compete for customers.\nWatch their moves each turn!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step11", "value": "Press SHOP to buy new, stronger cards.\nBetter cards = powerful combos = more profit!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step12", "value": "You're ready! Remember:\n- Combine cards for combos\n- Watch out for FBI with illegal cards\n- Expand your business empire!\n\nGood luck!"},
        {"key": "tutorial.next", "value": "Got it"},
